 />\n令支共侵台計劃難度又再提高<br />\n換咗屆就未必做到咁柒<br />\n林奠基本係專害支共同令香港人團結反政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ab84d4994e23d9119b4bf38ed4667fd6393e7b","tid":1227284,"uid":37232,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7e89b80822aa4ec40e524cc04e16b7a760e4cbf4","tid":1227284,"uid":179409,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"其實唔係好想佢落台<br />\n好難得有一個管治班底柒到咁盡<br />\n颱風事後公關處理極差<br />\n派4000蚊派到一鑊粥<br />\n推送中令反對派大團結<br />\n益埋蔡英文支持度暴昇<br />\n令支共侵台計劃難度又再提高<br />\n換咗屆就未必做到咁柒<br />\n林奠基本係專害支共同令香港人團結反政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"呢個都係想林鄭唔下台的原因之一<br />\n林鄭唔識政治，只識行政"},{"pid":"48c7dc7e008b4d39dbef53e02d1995cfb80345f5","tid":1227284,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e837ec51c25c7b801f94dacdf03c5981954c8a52","tid":1227284,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141b03139ab453f831bf2e575e4ac87a623119f4","tid":1227284,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229d50750982e45a943f7f3deda6ca5df24f11ee","tid":1227284,"uid":157453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:22:47.000Z","msg":"下一個會屌大力啲<br />\n<br />\n宜家繼續俾人強姦算數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4efc58faa3c